Most used SVN commands
----------------------

00) Get the whole sources from scratch:
svn checkout https://mplayer-amigaos.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ mplayer-amigaos

01) Update your copy:
svn update https://mplayer-amigaos.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/

02) Commit your changes:
svn commit -m "Text of changes."

03) Commit Message Correction:
svn propset -r 14 --revprop svn:log "First version of the benchmark suite added." https://mplayer-amigaos.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/

04) Revert all your local changes to the revision on the server:
svn revert --recursive .

05) Add or delete a file/directory
svn add (file)
svn delete (file)
